<section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 5px 15px 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">校友简介</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></span></section><section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><section><section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240321/1711028520299077460.jpg" title="1711028520299077460.jpg" alt="1711028520299077460.jpg" width="600" height="651" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 651px;"/></p><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;">朱晓波，男，汉族，籍贯江西九江。江西软件职业技术大学2005级软件设计专业校友，2008年取得江西师范大学本科学历，大学毕业后先后在上海罗亚国际物流公司、上海共繁国际物流公司工作，工作期间积累了一定的知识和经验。2012年创办上海德亚国际物流有限公司，从事进出口贸易的海运、空运、铁运运输等，现任上海德亚国际物流有限公司执行董事。</span></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></strong></p></section><section><p style="text-align: justify; text-indent: 2em;"></p><p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; display: inline-block; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: left;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">教育背景与职业起步</span></strong></p><p></p></section><section><section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240321/1711028567240073095.jpg" title="1711028567240073095.jpg" alt="1711028567240073095.jpg" width="600" height="450" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 450px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;">朱晓波在江西软件职业技术大学的软件设计专业接受了系统的教育和实训，在校还自考了江西师范大学本科学历，2009年孤身来到上海打拼，从事国际物流行业，从优秀新人到部门经理，再到全公司的销售冠军，2012年创办上海德亚国际物流有限公司经营至今，公司员工达到100人，年营业额达到1.1亿，公司旗下在九江、南京、南昌、安徽、德安等地均设有分公司。</span></p></section></section></section><section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;"><br/></span></strong></p><p><strong style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">对社会与行业的贡献</span></strong></p></section><section><section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240321/1711028601321022131.jpg" title="1711028601321022131.jpg" alt="1711028601321022131.jpg" width="600" height="400" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 400px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;">在担任上海德亚国际物流有限公司执行董事期间，他积极推动公司在进出口物流的创新与发展，特别是在进出口报关，进出口订舱，进出口集装箱三大业务板块的整合。这不仅极大地提高了公司的市场竞争力，也为推动相关行业的技术进步和商业模式创新做出了示范。通过公司的发展，带动了就业增长，促进了产业升级，对地方经济的发展产生了积极影响，为地方经济发展做出了积极贡献。此外，他还为教育发展助力，积极参与贫困学子的助学活动，慷慨助学。</span></p></section><section><section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section style="text-align: left;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">企业荣誉</span></strong></section></section></section><section><section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section><section><section><p style="text-align: center;"><img src="/data/upload/img/20240321/1711028630528086198.jpg" title="1711028630528086198.jpg" alt="1711028630528086198.jpg" width="600" height="450" border="0" vspace="0" style="width: 600px; height: 450px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;">上海德亚国际物流有限公司具有交通委的NVOCC资质，也是世界货代组织WIFFA及JCTRANS会员。</span></p></section><section><section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section></section><section><section><section><section style="text-align: left;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block;"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">校友寄语</span></strong></section></section></section><section><section><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section><section><section><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 16px;">“忆往昔，恩师言传身教诲人不倦；看今朝，母校桃李满园五湖四海，希望母校取得更辉煌的成绩，为国家培养更多的软件人才，为国家信息产业升级做出更大的贡献。”</span></p></section></section></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>